# (lua_newstate gained a seed parameter) — so prefer a 5.4 installation.
# Override with -DLUA_INCLUDE_DIR / -DLUA_LIBRARIES. Homebrew's prefix is not
# in every CMake's default search path — hint it, and probe the keg-only
# lua@5.4 directly (FindLua never looks inside opt/lua@5.4).
